query.value: SELECT address, applicationLocale, cellPhone, city, contactEmail, country, firstName, gender, homePhone, lastName, middleName, state, zip FROM JobApplication$${header.applicationTemplateId} WHERE id = '${header.applicationId}'
SELECT hiringManagerUserName FROM JobRequisition$${header.jobReqTemplateId} WHERE id = '${header.jobReqId}'
SELECT email FROM User WHERE username = '${header.hiringManagerUserName}'

SELECT applicationId, applicationTemplateId, assessmentPackageCode, candidateId, candidateTemplateId, clientId, createdBy, createdDate, handbackUrl, id, jobReqId, jobReqTemplateId, lastModifiedBy, lastModifiedDate, partnerId, vendorCode FROM AssessmentOrder WHERE id = '${header.assessmentOrderId}'
